            <p>If you have questions about your data or wish to exercise your rights under applicable privacy laws (GDPR, LGPD, CCPA/CPRA), please contact us through the platform’s support page.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="privacy-section">
            <h2>7. Public and private lists</h2>
            <p>The platform features curated public lists accessible and shareable by any visitor. Logged-in users can create private lists with item limits based on their subscription level. Private lists remain confidential unless shared externally by the user.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="privacy-section">
            <h2>8. Children and minors</h2>
